name: RAINDEER
description:
“There are some things, you were not meant to see. Such as tomorrow.”

She has many name, Dark Elf, Salpanas, Trazex, or Dew Ranger but her real name is Raindeer. 
She was an assassins from planet Dato02. She born on the cavern of agility, and she is a master of an archery.

She love a rain. A blue rain.
A thousand rain souls that she killed.
